      "widgets_values": ["Faithful Tile Upscale - Topaz / SeedV2 - 2x2\n\nPipeline: Tile Crop → Extract (×4) → [upscaler per tile] → Tile Collect → Tile Stitch → DPI export.\n\nAs saved, each tile uses Tile Scale By / Placeholder (AM) at 2× as a runnable stand-in.\nOnce the tiling and stitching look correct, replace each TileScaleByAM node with your\nreal upscaler (Topaz, SeedV2, ESRGAN, etc.) — the rest of the workflow stays identical.\n\ntile_metadata flows: TileCropAM → TileCollectAM (passthrough) → TileStitchAM.\nNo need to wire TileCropAM directly to TileStitchAM."]
